This app enables users to keep track of radio episodes they have listened to and identify those they haven't. It also offers features that allow users to organize episodes based on various criteria like genre, podcast series, and personal ratings, ensuring a streamlined and personalized listening journey.\",\"schema\":\"1. User Profile: Stores user information, preferences, and listening history.\\n2. Episode Database: Maintains records of all available radio episodes.\\n3. Listening Status Tracker: Keeps track of episodes as 'heard' or 'unheard'.\\n4. Episode Organizer: Allows categorization and prioritization of episodes based on user-defined criteria.\",\"layoutAndNavigation\":\"The app features a user-friendly dashboard that displays all the episodes categorized by their status (heard/unheard). Navigation is intuitive with tabs for different functionalities such as search, organize, and history.
